column2: SELECT TOP #  S.ObjID, S.z,S.sn_#  &&&, L2.ew ,L2.ewErr  &&&,L3.ew,L3.ewErr FROM SpecPhoto AS S   JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecObjAll AS sn ON S.SpecObjID = sn.SpecObjID WHERE L2.LineId = # and L3.LineID = # and (specclass=# or specclass=#) and S.zconf > .# and S.z < .#
